H0.text: What is the 3rd largest car rental company in the United States. Enterprise

H1.text: What is the 3rd largest car rental company in the United States. National

H2.text: What is the 3rd largest car rental company in the United States. Hertz

H3.text: What is the 3rd largest car rental company in the United States. Alamo

A4.text: Enterprise Holdings was one of the three big rental car holding companies in the United States, holding a 40% market share, placing it first, ahead of Hertz Global Holdings and Avis Budget Group.

A5.text: Hertz was second to Enterprise Holdings, placing it ahead of Avis Budget Group.

A6.text: Alamo typically caters to budget-conscious leisure travelers and is the largest car rental provider to international travelers visiting North America.
